Boy, that was a beauty. Now, come
on, honey. Let's you and me go places.

993
01:01:49,272 --> 01:01:51,263
No, no, Tommy!
Wait, Tommy.

994
01:01:51,340 --> 01:01:54,070
Tommy, no! I've got to get
that camera away from her.

